<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Annual Property Tax Calculation - {{taxYear}}</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; color: #1a1a1a; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f4f6f8; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 640px; margin: 24px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background: #0d47a1; color: #fff; padding: 24px 32px; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; }
    .content { padding: 32px; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; }
    th, td { padding: 12px 16px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0; }
    th { background: #f5f5f5; font-weight: 600; }
    td.amount { text-align: right; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
    .notice { background: #fff8e1; border-left: 4px solid #ffa000; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0; font-size: 14px; }
    .footer { background: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px 32px; font-size: 12px; color: #616161; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: #0d47a1; color: #fff !important; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; margin-top: 16px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>{{appName}} — Annual Tax Calculation {{taxYear}}</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear {{landlordName}},</p>
      <p>
        In accordance with <strong>Housing Proclamation No. 1320/2024</strong>, we have prepared
        your annual rental income tax calculation for the {{taxYear}} tax year. The figures below
        are based on registered lease contracts and long-term vacancy periods on your properties
        in Addis Ababa.
      </p>

      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Income type</th>
            <th class="amount">Amount (ETB)</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Rental income from occupied properties</td>
            <td class="amount">{{actualIncome}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Potential income from vacant periods (&gt;6 months)</td>
            <td class="amount">{{vacancyIncome}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Total taxable income</strong></td>
            <td class="amount"><strong>{{totalTaxableIncome}}</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Estimated tax</strong></td>
            <td class="amount"><strong>{{estimatedTax}}</strong></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <div class="notice">
        <strong>Important:</strong> This calculation is provided for <strong>information purposes only</strong>.
        You must pay your tax directly to the <strong>{{authorityName}}</strong> by
        <strong>{{paymentDeadline}}</strong>. This platform does <strong>NOT</strong> collect taxes
        on behalf of any government authority.
      </div>

      {{#if pdfUrl}}
      <p>
        <a class="btn" href="{{pdfUrl}}">Download PDF report</a>
      </p>
      {{/if}}

      <p>
        If you have questions about this calculation, please contact your sub-city housing office
        or the tax authority. Keep your registered lease documents for audit purposes.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>{{appName}} · Generated {{generatedDate}}</p>
      <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
